    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $33,500, a price that honestly reflects its good overall condition. The exterior presents well \u2014 paint is in decent shape with only minor scratches and light wear consistent with regular use, though it won't turn heads like a mint-condition vehicle. There are no major dents or rust issues, but close inspection will reveal the typical marks of a well-used car. The interior is clean and functional, with some wear on high-contact surfaces like the steering wheel, seat bolsters, and pedals. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained adequately \u2014 expect a solid, dependable daily driver rather than a showroom-fresh experience. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and HVAC \u2014 are in working order, though some components may benefit from attention in the near future. This is a practical, honest buy for someone looking for dependable transportation at a fair price, without paying a premium for perfection.",
